"guimenu><guimenuitem>Кірістіру</guimenuitem></menuchoice> таңдаңыз."

#. (itstool) path: listitem/para
#: C/index.docbook:1088
msgid ""
"Using the mouse You can also right click on the selected items in the drop down "
