"url=\"http://linux.die.net/man/5/dir_colors\">dir_colors man-бетінен</ulink> "
"қарауға болады."

#. (itstool) path: sect3/para
#: C/index.docbook:5238
msgid ""
"To enable the use of LS_COLORS for GNOME Commander click on "
